---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-dark-900/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-dark-700">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
        OneCyber<span class="text-primary-400">Logix</span>
      </a>
      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
        <a href="/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition">Home</a>
        <a href="/solutions" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition">Solutions</a>
        <a href="/about" class="text-primary-400 transition">About</a>
        <a href="/#contact" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition">Contact</a>
        <a href="/#contact" class="bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition">
          Get Started
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          About <span class="text-primary-400">OneCyberLogix</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          We're on a mission to transform how enterprises manage identity security through intelligent automation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-24">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-lg">
            <p>
              Founded by cybersecurity veterans who spent years in the trenches solving complex identity challenges, OneCyberLogix was born from a simple observation: traditional IAM solutions weren't keeping pace with modern threats.
            </p>
            <p>
              Enterprise identity management had become bloated, expensive, and reactive. Meanwhile, mid-market companies were left with either oversimplified tools or enterprise solutions they couldn't afford or implement.
            </p>
            <p>
              We saw an opportunity to change this — to build IAM solutions that are intelligent, autonomous, and accessible. Solutions that don't just enforce policies, but actively protect and optimize.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary-600/20 to-transparent rounded-3xl"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-dark-700/50 border border-dark-600 rounded-3xl p-10">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold">
                  CX
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold">TBD</h4>
                  <p class="text-primary-400">Founder & CEO</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="border-t border-dark-600 pt-6">
                <p class="text-gray-400 italic">
                  "I built OneCyberLogix to solve the problems I saw every day. Enterprises were drowning in manual IAM processes while threats evolved faster than they could respond. Agentic IAM isn't the future — it's the only way forward."
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Values -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Our <span class="text-primary-400">Values</span></h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Security First</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Every decision we make starts with security. We don't compromise on protecting what matters most — your identity infrastructure.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Innovation Always</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">The threat landscape evolves daily. We innovate continuously to stay ahead, bringing you the latest in AI-powered security.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Client Partnership</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">We're not just vendors — we're partners. Your success is our success, and we measure ourselves by your outcomes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Team -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Leadership</h2>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-md">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">
                CX
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">TBD</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-400 mb-4">Founder & CEO</p>
              <p class="text-gray-400">
                10+ years in cybersecurity, specializing in identity and access management, zero trust architecture, and cloud security. Previously led security programs at Fortune 500 companies.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-dark-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8">Let's discuss how we can secure your organization's identity infrastructure.</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="inline-block bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg transition-all hover:scale-105">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="py-8 bg-dark-900 border-t border-dark-700">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
          OneCyber<span class="text-primary-400">Logix</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">© 2026 OneCyberLogix. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
